r />\n陳補充，這些「加纖」茶，多是凍飲，凍飲會削弱脾胃功能，令脾虛夾濕，無論是脂肪型或水腫型肥胖，也不利減重。<br />\n<br />\n楊盈希補充，飲茶無助減肥，但茶的咖啡因及單寧有助刺激胃酸，可減輕餐後油膩感覺；如加入難消化性糊精，對減少熱量吸收有些少幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7c5e16d81589a584644d13af61594e35561c06","tid":769936,"uid":74898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59d3dd60d744a815621a0482295ff4c353741a68","tid":769936,"uid":51775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪即係叫你走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夠人唔會俾你踢囉 係咪要講到咁白呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 呢個一係就唔係friend 一係就係你真係太廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n都真係幾sad<br />\n我好似隻棋子同condom 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T02:06:57.000Z","msg":"yes u are"}]}